
            Video
            New York blast: 'Huge explosion and we heard screaming'
            At least 29 people have been injured in an explosion in New York City, officials say. Fire trucks and ambulances converged on the scene after what witnesses described as a "deafening" blast in the Chelsea district of Manhattan late on Saturday.Eyewitness Itay Cohai spoke to BBC News.
                
                        18 Sep 2016
                    
                
        
